import './LeftArrow.css';

const LeftArrow = (props) => {
    return (
        <svg className="last_news_invitation__arrow"
             xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 11 11" width="16"
             height="16">
            <g>
                <line stroke="#cccccc" stroke-width="1.3"
                      transform="rotate(84.62553405761719 8.262497901916504,7.598438262939455)"
                      id="svg_1" y2="10.06469" x2="10.358523" y1="5.132186"
                      x1="6.166473" fill="none"></line>
                <line stroke="#cccccc" stroke-width="1.3"
                      transform="rotate(-0.7916364073753357 5.622357845306128,5.731118202209512)"
                      id="svg_5" y2="5.806118" x2="10.336127" y1="5.656118"
                      x1="0.908589" fill-opacity="null" fill="none"></line>
                <line stroke="#cccccc" stroke-width="1.3"
                      transform="rotate(180 8.237500190734863,3.869054079055786)"
                      id="svg_6" y2="6.100001" x2="10.615028" y1="1.638108"
                      x1="5.859972" fill="none">
                </line>
            </g>
        </svg>
    )
}

export default LeftArrow;
